title: 2 BR near downtown, MIA, MCAD $1150 1/2 off Aug. rent.
app_fee: $20. Credit, criminal, and rental references checked.
posting_body: ["Large, bright 2 bedroom 1 bath apartment available in a classic 6 plex near Steven's Square, available 8/1.", "2nd floor unit: wood floors, oak wood work, updated kitchen dishwasher (classic original 1900's cabinets), gas range, built-in buffet in the dining room, entirely updated bath, tall ceilings, and a 3 season porch over looking 3rd Ave. (live in a treehouse!).", 'Off street parking first come first served, coin laundry and storage on-site.', 'Heat, water, and trash are included in the rent.', 'Tenant pays electric, phone, stove gas, and cable/internet.', 'Security deposit discounted 50% for great references and credit.', "Steven's Square Park and playground is within 1 block.", 'Walk downtown in 5 minutes.', 'Application fee is $20 per adult.', 'Good rental history required.', 'Household income 3X the monthly rent required.', 'Good credit is preferable.', 'No recent or serious convictions on your criminal background.', 'Cats and dogs okay!', 'No smoking in the apartment.', 'Please email for an appointment.', 'When you do please include some times that work for you for showings on or after 7/1.', 'Thanks!']
